  "prompt": "Which tickets were sold by BookMyShow for Global Citizen Festival?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, BookMyShow offered several types of tickets for the Global Citizen Festival to cater to different preferences and budgets. While the specific ticket categories and availability can vary based on the event location and date, here are some commonly available ticket types:\n\n1. **General Admission (GA):**\n   - **Description:** These tickets provide access to the general areas of the festival where attendees can enjoy performances from various artists.\n   - **Features:** Often the most affordable option, offering entry to the main stages and access to amenities like food stalls and merchandise booths.\n\n2. **VIP Passes:**\n   - **Description:** VIP tickets offer a more exclusive experience with additional perks.\n   - **Features:**\n     - Priority entry to the venue.\n     - Access to VIP lounges with complimentary refreshments.\n     - Reserved seating closer to the stage.\n     - Meet-and-greet opportunities with artists (subject to availability).\n\n3. **Premium Seating:**\n   - **Description:** These tickets provide enhanced seating arrangements with better views of the performances.\n   - **Features:** Reserved seats in designated premium sections, often accompanied by comfortable seating and sometimes included in hospitality packages.\n\n4. **Early Bird Tickets:**\n   - **Description:** Discounted tickets available for a limited time before the general sale begins.\n   - **Features:** Lower prices for attendees who purchase tickets early, subject to availability.\n\n5. **Group Tickets:**\n   - **Description:** Special packages designed for groups, such as families or corporate outings.\n   - **Features:** Discounts based on the number of tickets purchased together, sometimes including additional perks like reserved group seating.\n\n6. **Accessible Tickets:**\n   - **Description:** Tickets specifically arranged for attendees with disabilities.\n   - **Features:** Accessible seating locations, designated parking, and other accommodations to ensure a comfortable experience.\n\n7. **Add-Ons and Packages:**\n   - **Description:** Additional options that can be purchased alongside standard tickets.\n   - **Features:** Merchandise bundles, food and beverage vouchers, or exclusive memorabilia tied to the festival.\n\n**How to Purchase:**\n\nTo view the currently available ticket options, prices, and purchase tickets for the Global Citizen Festival through BookMyShow, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Visit the BookMyShow Website or App:**\n   - Go to [BookMyShow](https://in.bookmyshow.com/) on your browser or open the BookMyShow mobile app.\n\n2. **Search for Global Citizen Festival:**\n   - Use the search bar to locate the specific Global Citizen Festival event you're interested in.\n\n3. **Select Your Preferred Ticket Type:**\n   - Browse through the available ticket categories and select the one that best fits your needs.\n\n4. **Complete the Booking Process:**\n   - Follow the on-screen instructions to complete your purchase, which may include selecting seats, entering payment details, and receiving your e-tickets via email or the app.\n\n**Important Tips:**\n\n- **Check Availability Early:** Popular events like the Global Citizen Festival can sell out quickly, especially VIP and premium tickets.\n- **Review Refund and Exchange Policies:** Understand BookMyShow's terms in case you need to cancel or change your tickets.\n- **Stay Updated:** Visit the official Global Citizen Festival website or BookMyShow's event page for the latest information on dates, lineup, and ticket releases.\n\nIf you have specific questions or need assistance with your booking, you can contact BookMyShow's customer support through their website or app for personalized help.",
